Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-60,0:00:-03.-02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-03.00,0:00:00.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-16,0:00:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:40.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"North Block"\N"West Block" "South Block" "East Block"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings of those who are in anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are crushed by a dry cloud of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those who seek hope,\Nand those who cling to hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their feelings cross each other,\Nuncertain what to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,marking an era of history ending in sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:02:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile tries to get information\Non where the Poneglyph is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and announces that a cannonball\Nwill be shot into the Palace Square.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this be the end of Alabasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will there be real peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sandglass of fate starts\Nthe final countdown once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Battle Is Over!\NKoza Raises The White Flag"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our way!\NOut of our way! Out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Chaka-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...? Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kicking Claw Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:03:02.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alabasta Kingdom Elite Guard Unit\NKicking Claw Force"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They broke the door!\NIt's the Kicking Claw Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Just as you'd expect from the elite troops!\N--Please save His Majesty and Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty! Defending you\Nto the death is our mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just stay away from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When dealing with one of\Nthe Seven Warlords of the Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have to do whatever\Nit takes, even if it's unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All four of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will fight together...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to set things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you are very popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spare you, so go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No can do.\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason that we can't withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:04:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really are the ringleader\Nof this whole rebellion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bruises...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't bother. They're worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka! Something is wrong with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to boost their\Npower temporarily... they...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they drank the water that\Nshortens their lives... the fatal fuel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They only have a few minutes left to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't be saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought as much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Challenging me at the cost\Nof your own lives...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka-sama... Please forgive us\Nfor doing this without consulting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:05:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we have to make him\Nrealize... this country's pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make him...\Nrealize this country's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should value your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:06:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's too late, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna die anyway, I don't\Neven have to kill you myself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't even bother fighting...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka... sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the very definition of stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wicked fiend...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka! Stop it!\NDon't follow them to their deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... A Zoan type...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog Dog Fruit, Model Jackal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Howling Fangs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the type...\Nwho'd die for others, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:31.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alubarna - North Block\NIn front of the Mehdi Assembly Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I bled too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm lucky that\Nthe wounds aren't deep...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it does... hit me hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how the others are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one'd better be dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I have to pair with Lashes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:08:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a camel, for god's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate how weak I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because you were unlucky\Nin the raffle! Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! Then promise me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we're in a pinch...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you save us, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy. I only save ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp. Why're you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you saying is crying?! Crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who says someone's\Ncrying is actually crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mole hag said... that Luffy's dead, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I wonder if it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! Are you stupid or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither! I don't believe it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right already! Then what we have\Nto do now is get to the palace ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stow your snot away until the\Nrumbling of this battle stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't swallow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to thank us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. Besides, if you\Nwanna thank pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you have to let us see some goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you trying to\Nleach out of this country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nami okay...? Did she get away okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.91,0:09:39.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alubarna - North Block\NBehind the Mehdi Assembly Hall"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... They finally came off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what he meant by\Na powerful one-shot attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wave of rebels is already\Nright around the corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:10:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...though the situation has changed....\NIn any case, I should head to the palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with Vivi...?\NThe battle seems to have started...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Vivi-chan. Just remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a battle... that guy eats tons...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting for you in Alubarna, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this will be the crucial point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't goof things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! See you at the Alubarna Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being weak... is a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:22.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Palace Square\N25 minutes to the explosion time"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K... Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... I see, you came through\Nthe shortcut you used to use...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:12:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong with my eyes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to persuade the Royal Army, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king is... about to be\Nkilled by the country's hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe what I'm seeing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has become interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the middle of the battle right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet both sides' leaders\Nare facing each other here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This war is now a fight to the death
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between lizards whose heads are broken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're confused.\NWell, that's just a natural reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just imagine the worst possible scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold suspicion, Koza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I was born here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! Who took the rain\Naway from this country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me, Koza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you thought\Nwas the king's doing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was a "trap" by my company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over the past two years, you guys\Nplayed right into our hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:14:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when the royal family and army\Nwere desperately chasing our shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably could've died happy\Nif you didn't know this fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't listen to him, Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still things you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save as many citizens as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within less than half an hour...\Nthe Palace Square will be blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Move, Vivi! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Square will become a battlefield.\NIf it really gets blown up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... I won't let it become a battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still panicking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will happen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if they realize now that\Nthe Square'll be blown up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't just be a panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once that happens, the war will\Nno longer stop! No one will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... what a clever judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we should do was\Ndecided from the beginning...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is to stop this plotted rebellion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:16:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the only one who can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you think I'll just sit back and watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am... the Jackal, Alabasta's guardian deity!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who destroys the\Nenemies of the royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:17:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I still live, I fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you call "stupidity."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you want, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can probably hold him back\Nat least for a few more minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaka...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the leader of\NSand Sand Clan isn't all that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?! You're childish!\NTake it easy on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pain in the neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who asked me to train you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Report from Guard Unit 2 to Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Report from Unit 2 to Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Line 4... has been broken through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rebel army is currently\Npassing through the Central Plaza
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and heading to the North Block!\NThey'll reach the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the white flag to surrender!\NSurrender right now...! Royal Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama! What's she saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do such a thing, what's\Ngonna happen to this country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Koza! Why is the rebel army's leader here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.90,0:18:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to Vivi! We no longer\Ndesire victory, or to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stop this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will let the rebel army know...\Nthat this battle was pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that there's no longer\Na reason for us to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order not to shed any more\Npointless blood, wave the white flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king's head is close at hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! We can now see the clock tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're approaching the Palace Square!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:20:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White flags?! The Royal Army is\Nwaving white flags to surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Koza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Koza-san doing here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza-san... What is Koza-san\Ndoing here...? Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Subdue your anger\Nand drop your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Army no longer\Nhas the will to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true...? Koza-san...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... the battle is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction should I run towards\Nto see a more wonderful tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.89,0:22:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the helm and opened the\Nmiraculous map that I stored in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.66,0:22:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I aimed for the sky and sought out\Nmy dreams, though at times I got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a dream; when I met you,\NI discovered the wonderful person in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a bit of courage,\NI gained something grand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time for my "wish"\Nto become my "pledge"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.85,0:22:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sketch out the tale of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put all my feelings\Nin a brand new wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never-ending journey to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase after you\Nwherever you go, Shining ray
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:23:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Princess. You can't save the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.22,0:23:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My voice no longer reaches anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done, the country will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Your voice is heard by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna put an end... to all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where Vivi's Voice Gets Heard!\NThe Hero Descends!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.07,0:23:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
